The paper deals with the task of audio captioning, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The dataset creation involves sound processing and annotation, which suggests sub-categories cs.SD (Sound) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of crowdsourcing and post-processing techniques for data cleaning suggests sub-categories cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
